snippet.title: How to Multiply Decimals
snippet.description:
Learn How to Multiply Decimals in this video.  We go through 3 examples in this free math video tutorial by Mario's Math Tutoring.

0:25 Example 1 Multiply 8.2 x 6
1:00 Count the Number of Decimal Places
1:15 Example 2 Multiply 4.5 x 2.7
2:16 Example 3 Multiply 9.8 x .21
